title: In-debth Bible Study in the Book of Revelation in HD
description:
This is a complete study through the book of Revelation taught by Pastor Brett Meador of Athey Creek Christian Fellowship in Wilsonville Oregon
Athey Creek Christian Fellowship is a body of believers in Wilsonville Oregon desiring to know the Lord in an ever-increasing measure. We are a non- denominational fellowship associating with all who are in the Body of Christ.

66-1 The Book of Blessing - REVELATION 1:3 by BRETT MEADOR|March 24th, 2013
Be blessed as we read through Revelation! We are introduced to this final book of the Bible by learning the author of Revelation, understanding the main point is Jesus Christ. As we examine common misconceptions of Revelation, take on the joy, peace and comfort welling in this book of prophecy.
